title: LIVE AT 11: The Suburban Ford 7 Sports Cave
text:
Previous Next 
(WXYZ) - The Suburban Ford 7 Sports Cave is back after a big weekend in college football, and an even bigger weekend ahead. 
Watch the show live at 11 a.m. by clicking here 
This week, Justin Rose is joined by Dan Leach from 97.1 The Ticket and Rico Beard from Detroit Sports 105.1. 
With both Michigan and Michigan State winning on Saturday, it sets up a big matchup between the two teams this Saturday. 
Plus, the 0-4 Lions are preparing to take on the 3-1 Arizona Cardinals on Sunday afternoon, and the guys will preview the upcoming game. 
Remember, you can join the conversation on Twitter using the hashtag #7SportsCave.
